data.description: Spacious 5 bedroom home in a cul-de-sac in a highly sought after area, neighborhood and school districts is now available and ready for move in! Home has been under home warranty since purchase and negotiable to transfer and convey. New roof, new hvac and new duct work in 2020! 2 zoned heating and cooling systems. Tons of storage in attic and oversized garage. Fully fenced in back yard with nice size deck. Formal dining room and eat-in kitchen. Formal living room and a family room with wood burning fireplace. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Laundry room / mud room off garage with half bath and enough space to renovate into full bathroom on first floor. Excellent community with no association fees. Centrally located and easy access to interstates, military bases, greenbrier shopping, town center and beaches. Shed and extra fridge in good condition to convey as-is. Ring security camera to convey. Inquire with agent about negotiating to buy down interest rate with preferred lender!
